<scenario>
The agent A provided the following violation scenario:When OS_DEBUG is defined as an empty macro (as shown: #define OS_DEBUG(__VA_ARGS__)), the statement OS_DEBUG("Implementation failed to initialize tick time globals\n"); preprocessor-expands to a null statement (no-op). This is executed but has no effect and could be removed without changing program behaviour (in that build configuration), therefore it constitutes dead code and violates MISRA C 2023 Rule 2.2.
</scenario>
